Package: dragenCNVreader
Type: Package
Title: Read and Parse DRAGEN CNV VCF Files
Version: 0.2.2
Authors@R: person(
    given = "Yiming",
    family = "Jiang",
    email = "zbjiangyiming@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Reads CNV (copy-number variation) VCF files produced by the
    Illumina DRAGEN secondary-analysis pipeline. Parses the multi-key
    FORMAT field (GT, CN, MCN, CNQ, MCNQ, CNF, MCNF, MF, SM, SD, MAF,
    BC, AS, PE) into separate columns, normalises the DRAGEN ALT codes
    (DEL/DUP/LOH/REF/INV/INS/BND, plus the VCF missing marker '.' which
    DRAGEN uses for reference segments) into a tidy 'cnv' category
    (loss / gain / cn-LOH / LOH / ref / inv / ins / bnd), and returns
    both the PASS-only and the full call set as data frames. Unsupported
    ALT codes raise an error. Optionally writes the parsed tables to
    disk via 'out_dir' / 'out_type'. Single-file and recursive batch
    modes are supported.
